{"pageProps":{"article":{"title":"Meal Prep Monday: Vegan Coconut Curry","category":"On the Menu","subcategory":"Recipes","publish_date":"2018-10-22T07:00:00.000Z","full_thumbnail":"https://i0.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/IMG_6610.jpg?resize=355%2C230&ssl=1","mobile_thumbnail":"https://i0.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/IMG_6610.jpg?resize=980%2C647&ssl=1","description":"Try this tasty meal that will decrease your environmental footprint.","content":"<div class=\"single-post-content\">\n            <p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">This week, I made a vegan coconut curry. While vegans tend to get some flak, decreasing your meat intake is an easy way to decrease your environmental footprint. Curries are so versatile and easily customizable and are perfect for vegans and carnivores alike. </span></p>\n<div id=\"attachment_84379\" style=\"width: 1034px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-84379\" data-attachment-id=\"84379\" data-permalink=\"https://dailynexus.com/2018-10-22/meal-prep-monday-vegan-coconut-curry/img_6610/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/IMG_6610.jpg?fit=2048%2C1365&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"2048,1365\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta='{\"aperture\":\"0\",\"credit\":\"\",\"camera\":\"\",\"caption\":\"\",\"created_timestamp\":\"0\",\"copyright\":\"\",\"focal_length\":\"0\",\"iso\":\"0\",\"shutter_speed\":\"0\",\"title\":\"\",\"orientation\":\"0\"}' data-image-title=\"IMG_6610\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/IMG_6610.jpg?fit=250%2C167&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/IMG_6610.jpg?fit=888%2C592&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"size-large wp-image-84379\" src=\"https://i2.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/IMG_6610-1024x683.jpg?resize=888%2C592\" alt=\"\" width=\"888\" height=\"592\" sr